The error message "SyntaxError: JSON.parse: unexpected character at line 1 column 1 of the JSON data" typically occurs when the data returned from the API endpoint is not in a valid JSON format.

To troubleshoot this issue, you can:

1. Check the response from the API directly:

```javascript
const response = await fetch('http://localhost:5000/api/chat');
const responseData = await response.text();
console.log(responseData);
